N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1633.1 - Scope

State Regulations

This Part relates to the funding of drug elimination
programs pursuant to the Public Housing Drug Elimination Pilot Program, article
XII, Public Housing Law, as added by chapter 713 of the Laws of 1990. The
applicability of this Part is conditioned on receipt of funding by the division
and the division's publication of a notice of funding
availability. Notes
